{:component/id :orbiplex/tls-trust-policy
 :component/title "TLS Trust Policy"
 :component/type :node-transport-trust-layer
 :component/status :partial

 :summary
 "Node-side TLS trust layer that separates endpoint transport verification,
 signed endpoint evidence, peer identity proof, capability authorization, and
 local operator policy. It covers service CA material, Seed Directory endpoint
 evidence, advisory TLS route ids, local listener certificate generation, and
 peer supervisor enforcement."

 :must-implement
